

# Encryption Program

This is a java desktop program based onSwing GUI widget toolkit for Java to encrypt and decrypt the message using one-time pad (OTP) is an encryption technique that cannot be cracked, but requires the use of a single-use pre-shared key that is not smaller than the message being sent.


## Functionality


The user enters the message through text field label
The program will generate a random key
The program will convert both the paintext (message) and random key to binary system
The program will apply XOR logical operator in binary system to generate Cipher
The cipherBinary will be converted to text will be displayed in screen
Decryption will happens and convert to origin message
The origin message will be displayed in the screen
If the user want to verify again it will not because the key is valid once
Exit the program through close button in top left of the screen



